OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread from the southwest during this
OL,7,Fevening and for a time in the early
OL,8,Fhours. Drier weather developing across
OL,9,Fmost areas later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA dry and mostly cloudy day.
OL,12,FSome brightness breaking through
OL,13,Facross Fife and the Central Belt at
OL,14,Ftimes. Mild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,17,FCloudy, mild with rain on Wednesday,
OL,18,Fdrier with a few showers later.
OL,19,FBright, breezy with scattered showers
OL,20,Fon Thursday, mainly dry in the east.
OL,21,FRain for a time on Friday.
